*[[1913]] &amp;ndash; [[Richard Stone]], British economist, [[Bank of Sweden Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel|Nobel laureate]] (d. 1991)
*[[1915]] &amp;ndash; [[Robert Strassburg]], American composer (d. 2003)
