*[[1938]] &amp;ndash; [[Max Factor, Sr.]], Polish-born American make-up artist and cosmetic manufacturer (b. 1877)
*[[1940]] &amp;ndash; [[J.J. Thomson]], English physicist, [[Nobel Prize in Physics|Nobel laureate]] (b. 1856)
*[[1941]] &amp;ndash; [[Peder Oluf Pedersen]], Danish engineer and physicist (b. 1874)
*[[1943]] &amp;ndash; Father [[Eustáquio van Lieshout]], Dutch Catholic priest (b. 1890)
*[[1946]] &amp;ndash; [[Konstantin Rodzaevsky]], Russian fascist (executed) (b. 1907)
*[[1949]] &amp;ndash; [[Arthur Fielder]], English cricketer (b. 1877)
*[[1961]] &amp;ndash; [[Charles Coburn]], American actor (b. 1877)
*[[1963]] &amp;ndash; [[Guy Burgess]], English-born Soviet spy (b. 1911)
