*[[1991]] &amp;ndash; [[Jean Tinguely]], Swiss painter and sculptor (b. 1925)
*[[1993]] &amp;ndash; [[Richard Jordan]], American actor (b. 1938)
*[[1994]] &amp;ndash; [[Lindsay Anderson]], English film director (b. 1923)
*[[1995]] &amp;ndash; [[Fischer Black]], American economist (b. 1938)
