      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Redirect|Lavoisier}}
{{Infobox scientist
|name        = Antoine Lavoisier
|image       = Antoine lavoisier color.jpg
|caption     = Line engraving by Louis Jean Desire Delaistre, after a design by Julien Leopold Boilly
