*[[1893]] &amp;ndash; [[Violette Morris]], French athlete (d. 1944)
*[[1897]] &amp;ndash; [[Ardito Desio]], Italian topographer (d. 2001)
*[[1901]] &amp;ndash; [[Al Lewis (lyricist)|Al Lewis]], American lyricist (d. 1967)
*  1901   &amp;ndash; [[László Németh]], Hungarian writer (d. 1975)
*  1901   &amp;ndash; [[Elene Akhvlediani]], Georgian artist (d. 1975)
*[[1902]] &amp;ndash; [[Giuseppe Pella]], [[Prime Minister of Italy]] (d. 1981)
