*[[1904]] &amp;ndash; [[Pigmeat Markham]], American comedian (d. 1981)
*[[1905]] &amp;ndash; [[George H. Hitchings]], American scientist, [[Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine|Nobel laureate]] (d. 1998)
