===Criticism===
* [http://missourifolkloresociety.truman.edu/remedy.html Davis, Adam Brooke. &quot;A Few Words About Folk Medicine/&quot;] Folklorist argues against uncritical use of traditional healing practices, especially by non-members of the cultures which generate the traditions
